{{Quote|Can't identify the exact religion; I guess I shouldn't have skipped so much Sunday school as a kid.|Han Solo|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 7">[[Star Wars (1977) 7|''Star Wars'' (1977) 7]]</ref>}}
'''Sunday school''' was a form of religious education. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] frequently skipped it as a child, and used this as an excuse for being unable to identify the religion of a [[Priest/Legends|priest]] [[Pera]] of the [[Sacred Way/Legends|Sacred Way]].

